Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是山賊的碉堡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.23,0:00:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 攻破這裡就是你們狩人的第一件大任務
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作戰計劃如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正義之士要堂堂正正地…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從正面出擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…為什麼連我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你是狩人的候補啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多看看大家的工作比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是殺了希爾的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要忍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥也說過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有熱情是不夠的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要想辦法逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把情報傳遞給大家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…不正是逃走的機會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:00:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺根本逃不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.33,0:01:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從正面攻擊 膽量不小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.87,0:01:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小可 5號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.71,0:01:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十王之裁決
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.09,0:01:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正義閻魔槍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個 7號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.18,0:01:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正義·泰山炮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的兵器是由我做出來的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.60,0:01:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神之手「完美」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能將手指的精密動作提升數百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對是最時尚的帝具哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部收拾掉之後再拼起來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人偶們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 不用謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是一個團隊嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我早察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:01:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰放射器帝具
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.27,0:02:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煉獄招來「虹色風燈」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也算工作之一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天…使…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼之帝具 萬里飛翔「憎惡」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能放過任何一個人
